    "chunk_index": 0,
    "chunk_text": "Recap. Apart from all the fancy words used here, the Dependency Injection system is quite simple. Just functions that look the same as the path operation functions . But still, it is very powerful, and allows you to declare arbitrarily deeply nested dependency \"graphs\" (trees).",
